"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-09-olympic-champion-vows-quit-punched-kicked-face-21394545\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Olympichero Daniel Wiffen has revealed the 10km marathon swim is 'one of the worst things' he's ever done after getting 'punched in the face' mid-race.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 151, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 23-year-oldbecame the first male swimmer to win goldforIrelandlast week when he was crowned the 800m freestyle champion inParis.\", \"from\": 153, \"to\": 285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He also went on to win bronze in the 1500m freestyle final five days later.\", \"from\": 287, \"to\": 362, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wiffen made his open water swimming debut today and finished in a respectable 18th place in the 10km event through the River Seine.\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 483, \"end\": 494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he's issued a brutally honest verdict on how it went and said he's already 'retiring' from this particular competition.\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 620, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When asked how he felt after his first open water swim, Wiffen joked: 'And last, and last.'\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 713, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's one of the worst things I have ever done,' he told RTE Sport.\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 772, \"end\": 781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999999989440767, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RTE Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m never doing it again\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009dDaniel Wiffen absolutely delighted he finished the 10km marathon swim in the Seine and announces his retirement from \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098open water\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 \\u00e2\\u0098\\u0098\\u00ef\\u00b8\\u008fpic.twitter.com/QIap4fIQ5W  'But yeah, I am happy I did it.\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 896, \"end\": 901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999983745056, \"rank\": 1.6096102882149265e-09, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now I can say that I can range from 10k.\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1059, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'And I actually placed higher than I did in Tokyo in the pools so I am pretty proud of myself.\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1105, \"end\": 1110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999958968728656, \"rank\": 3.223078821607345e-06, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But, you know, when you get to halfway, all I was thinking was \\\"I am already an Olympic champion and I am swimming this and I am coming 18th\\u2026\\\"  'I was like, \\\"oh I will just finish it now, but then I am never doing it again\\\".'\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1383, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wiffen was also taken aback by the brutal nature of the open water swim and says he much prefers the less chaotic pool events after taking a few hits to the face.\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1547, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'All the coaches are laughing because I was swimming out by myself because I wasn't arsed going behind somebody,' he said.\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1671, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'All I was thinking was \\\"yeah, I can not be arsed to get kicked in the face\\\".\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1750, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I got a couple of elbows in the eye and I got punched in the face at one point.\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1832, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'This sport is not for me I do not think.\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1875, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I definitely want my own lane next time.'\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1917, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wiffen, who finished the race in just under two hours, said he even considered 'pulling out' beforehand but 'wanted to do it because my friends are'.\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 2068, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I did not actually see any of them apart from my training partner Toby [Robinson] from GB,' he joked.\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2158, \"end\": 2160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9810325942751127, \"rank\": 0.019301524158368392, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'My goal coming into this was to finish and I am very pleased with myself and happy to say I did not come last, so that's the main thing.\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2311, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am so happy I have completed it and I am retiring from open water.'\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2383, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Reflecting on his incredible time at the Olympics, he added: 'I could not ask for anything more.\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2481, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Becoming an Olympic champion ages ago now it seems, about a week-and-a-half ago, and then a bronze medal as well.\", \"from\": 2483, \"to\": 2597, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We do not really have athletes winning any medals, so to come away with two\\u2026 amazing.\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2685, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am looking forward to the homecoming on Monday.'\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2738, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2788, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2860, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Team GB teenager dubbed 'The Terminator' clinches historic Olympic gold in Paris  ArrowMORE:Olympic water polo player left bloody after gruesome eye injury  ArrowMORE:'Drunk' Olympic wrestler arrested for sexual assault in Paris  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 3212, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2947, \"end\": 2952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999993095571, \"rank\": 6.9044968056477945e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3095, \"end\": 3100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999993095571, \"rank\": 6.9044968056477945e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 3214, \"to\": 3345, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 3346, \"to\": 3518, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3408, \"end\": 3414, \"title\": 